text: Marusarz is a Polish surname typical for Goral population of Zakopane region. Notable people include: * Józef Marusarz (1926-1996), Polish alpine skier * Stanisław Marusarz (1913-1993), Polish Nordic-combined skier * Wojciech Marusarz (born 1993), Polish Nordic-combined skier Category:Polish-language surnames
title: Marusarz
